Package: ROCsurvcomp
Title: ROC-Based Methods for Comparing Survival Distributions with Right, Left, and Doubly Censored Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-30
Authors@R: c(person("Mohammod Mahmudur", "Rahman", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "mahmudur.asif13@gmail.com"),
             person("Leonidas", "Bantis", role = "aut",
             email = "lbantis@kumc.edu"))
Maintainer: Mohammod Mahmudur Rahman <mahmudur.asif13@gmail.com>
Description: Implements ROC-length, overlap coefficient (OVL), and joint ROC length-OVL-based methods for comparing survival distributions under non-proportional hazards (non-PH). The methods do not require any prior knowledge of the underlying non-PH pattern, and can accommodate right, left, and doubly censored data.
